        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 2. (a) Selenops banksi, paratype male, from Panama (MCZ) (b) S. banksi, holotype male, from Panama (MCZ 20436) (c) S. banksi, ex-S. kikay syn. nov., holotype male, from Itabuna, Brazil (MNRJ – destroyed) (d) S. banksi, female described here, from Orellana, Ecuador (NMNH) (e) S. banksi, female, ventral, Orellana, Ecuador (NMNH) (f) S. banksi, male, Orellana, Ecuador (NMNH) (g) S. banksi, male, ventral, Orellana, Ecuador (different specimen than f but in same vial) (NMNH) (h) S. banksi, male, Rio Tambopata Reserve, Madre de Dios, Peru (MCZ) (i) S. banksi, male, Iwokrama,Guyana (CAS 9058003) (j) S. curruganja sp. nov., holotype female, Corpoica, Tumaco, Dept. Nariño, Colombia, (ICN-Ar-8289) (k) S. ducke, holotype male, sternum (MCN 25527) (l) S. ducke, paratype female, sternum (MCN 21487) (m)" ;
